          The CommsControllerIF defines a component that centralizes the handling of all Dark Matter Protocol messages.
ErrorOptionsEnum
          The ErrorOptionsEnum indicates, for DMP or PC errors how the error handling will be performed.
EventHandlerIF
          The EventHandlerIF allows for sending events back through centralized handler on components that perform get requests with an EVENTS option.
ResponseCallback
          The ResponseCallback class provides a common base for asynchronous callback handlers that handle each type of Dark Matter Protocol message.
ResponseHandlerIF
          The ResponseHandlerIF allows us to funnel all responses and associated errors back through a single handler interface.
